    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive wide-body 996.2 featuring a 3.6L flat-six mated to a 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically flawless, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed cooling system with a low-temperature thermostat. The AWD system utilizes a viscous center coupling for precise torque distribution, complemented by the factory-spec Turbo-derived braking system and suspension. Every panel retains its original finish with zero evidence of oxidation or road rash. The cabin presents in a true time-capsule state, with impeccable leather surfaces and fully functional switchgear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and fastidious maintenance.",
      "price": 44900.0,
